ZhiZu.io(
========
My personal website, where I record some of my thoughts and write articles; I also maintain a blog there.

Website:
--------

    https://ioit-aaa.github.io

To build this documentation, use:

    mkdocs build

Commands for repo owner
-----------------------

Push to gh-pages branch:
------------------------

    mkdocs gh-deploy

Within the root directory of the source code, there is also a script containing the aforementioned steps. This script was written to facilitate the release of website modifications.
)
